{"type":"message","id":"062188c5","parentId":"76f0669b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:12:07.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK jadi Sentra ini software house tempat Lucy kerja sebagai PM. Sekarang gw lihat gambar lebih detail — ini slide \"Ekosistem FMS (Software)\" dari Sentra.\n\nFitur yang di-klaim di slide:\n1. Lisensi Platform Dasbor FMS Sentra (Akses Penuh)\n2. Analitik Konsumsi BBM & Prediksi Kebocoran\n3. Modul Laporan Ritase (Cycle Time Analysis)\n4. Pemantauan Kesehatan Mesin via CAN-Bus (J1939)\n5. Analitik Perilaku Supir (HSE Metrics)\n6. Integrasi Data Multi-Device (Web & Mobile)\n\nHarga: Rp 1.250.000/Unit/Bulan"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_rxKZWoCMYule0uISZkMrG5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/bin/search \"Sentra Vidya Utama SEVIMA FMS fleet management mining\" 2>&1 | head -30; echo \"===\"; ~/bin/search \"\\\"sentra\\\" software fleet management CAN-Bus J1939 mining Indonesia product\" 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":15}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":346,"cacheRead":86917,"cacheWrite":332,"totalTokens":87596,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00865,"cacheRead":0.0434585,"cacheWrite":0.002075,"total":0.054188499999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775020318291}}
