{"type":"message","id":"03eb1a86","parentId":"5fc44b55","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:14:07.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Oke gw udah cek. Sitenya *ada* — fms.sentratechnology.com live, redirect ke /login, built with Laravel + Metronic template. Company site sentratechnology.com juga live (Nuxt.js).\n\nJadi produknya beneran exist, bukan vaporware. Gw tarik balik skeptis gw soal itu.\n\nTapi yang bisa gw lihat dari luar cuma halaman login doang — nggak ada public demo, nggak ada fitur page, nggak ada docs API. Jadi gw nggak bisa verify fitur-fitur spesifik yang di-klaim di slide itu (CAN-Bus J1939, prediksi kebocoran BBM, cycle time analysis, dll) tanpa akses ke dalamnya.\n\nLo mau gw cek apa spesifik soal ini? Kalau lo punya login credentials gw bisa explore dashboardnya, atau kalau lo mau gw bantu validasi dari sisi teknis apakah klaim-klaim di slide itu masuk akal."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":279,"cacheRead":92078,"cacheWrite":3775,"totalTokens":96133,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.006975,"cacheRead":0.046039,"cacheWrite":0.02359375,"total":0.07661275}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775020436083}}
