{"type":"message","id":"ea5bfb95","parentId":"9f74aed1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:25:44.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke, gw udah dapet gambaran lengkap. Sekarang gw cocokin sama brosur.\n\nIni hasilnya:\n\n**Brosur vs Web Demo FMS Sentra:**\n\n**1. Lisensi Platform Dasbor FMS** ✅ Ada\n— Dashboard lengkap, live tracking 50 unit, peta Leaflet, status kendaraan (Engine Off/Idle/Move/Offline)\n\n**2. Analitik Konsumsi BBM & Prediksi Kebocoran** ⚠️ Sebagian\n— Ada menu \"Fuel Report\" di bawah Report, tapi gw belum bisa konfirmasi sejauh mana isinya (prediksi kebocoran atau cuma log konsumsi biasa)\n\n**3. Modul Laporan Ritase (Cycle Time Analysis)** ✅ Ada\n— Ada \"Trip Report\" di menu Report, plus \"Trip\" dan \"Performance\" di Dashboard\n\n**4. Pemantauan Kesehatan Mesin via CAN-Bus (J1939)** ❓ Nggak kelihatan\n— Nggak ada menu khusus engine diagnostics / CAN-Bus / health monitoring. Mungkin data-nya masuk lewat GPS tracker tapi nggak ada halaman dedicated buat liat parameter mesin\n\n**5. Analitik Perilaku Supir (HSE Metrics)** ⚠️ Sebagian\n— Ada \"Intervention\" dan \"Intervention Report\" (kemungkinan harsh braking, speeding, dll). Ada juga \"Face Recognize\" buat driver ID. Tapi nggak ada label eksplisit \"HSE Metrics\" atau scoring supir\n\n**6. Integrasi Data Multi-Device (Web & Mobile)** ⚠️ Web aja\n— Web-nya responsive, tapi gw nggak liat link ke mobile app (Play Store/App Store). Bisa jadi ada tapi nggak di-expose di web\n\n**Bonus fitur di web yang NGGAK ada di brosur:**\n- Live Streaming (CCTV?)\n- Face Recognition\n- Panic button\n- Geofence (zona virtual)\n- Heatmap\n- Post-event analysis\n- Maintenance module\n- Driver to Vehicle assignment\n\n**Kesimpulan:** Sekitar 2 dari 6 fitur brosur udah jelas ada. 3 ada sebagian, 1 (CAN-Bus engine health) nggak kelihatan. Tapi web demo-nya punya banyak fitur *extra* yang nggak disebut di brosur.\n\nMau gw buka halaman-halaman spesifik (Fuel Report, Trip, Performance) buat konfirmasi lebih detail?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":688,"cacheRead":29185,"cacheWrite":1473,"totalTokens":31347,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0172,"cacheRead":0.0145925,"cacheWrite":0.009206250000000001,"total":0.04100375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775021126107}}
