{"type":"message","id":"dcb76af6","parentId":"5ce727a6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:26:20.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nUdah gw cocokin bro. Cek reply gw barusan di atas — ringkasnya:\n\n- **2 dari 6** fitur brosur udah jelas ada (Dashboard + Ritase/Trip)\n- **3** ada sebagian (BBM, Perilaku Supir, Multi-Device)\n- **1** nggak kelihatan sama sekali (CAN-Bus engine health)\n\nTapi web demo-nya punya bonus fitur kayak Live Streaming, Face Recognition, Panic button, Geofence, Heatmap yang nggak ada di brosur.\n\nMau gw drill down lebih dalam ke halaman tertentu?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":172,"cacheRead":30098,"cacheWrite":2826,"totalTokens":33099,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0043,"cacheRead":0.015049,"cacheWrite":0.0176625,"total":0.037026500000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775021174825}}
