{"type":"message","id":"36e47bac","parentId":"4d81aeff","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:30:46.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAh oke, gw liat — space di brosurnya emang kecil. Bullet points-nya cuma muat beberapa baris pendek di bawah \"Termasuk :\".\n\nGw bikin versi yang super ringkas, cocok buat space segitu:\n\n---\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Dashboard real-time & live GPS tracking\n• Laporan ritase, BBM & performa armada\n• Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi otomatis\n• Live streaming CCTV & face recognition\n• Geofence, panic alert & heatmap\n• Akses multi-device (desktop, tablet, HP)\n\n---\n\n6 bullet, pendek-pendek, muat di space kecil. Mau ditambahin/dikurangin atau ganti kata-katanya?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":206,"cacheRead":33554,"cacheWrite":1417,"totalTokens":35180,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00515,"cacheRead":0.016777,"cacheWrite":0.008856250000000001,"total":0.03079825}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775021439512}}
