{"type":"message","id":"eb8b7048","parentId":"fa993912","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:42:24.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nItu tagline singkat di bawah judul produk kan? Harusnya ngejelasin *value proposition* produk itu dalam 1 kalimat.\n\nBuat \"Custom Landing Page, Web App & Mobile App\" — beberapa opsi:\n\n1. **Solusi digital lengkap untuk bisnis Anda.**\n2. **Dari website hingga aplikasi, semua dalam satu paket.**\n3. **Wujudkan ide bisnis Anda ke dunia digital.**\n4. **Satu paket, semua platform — web, mobile, siap pakai.**\n5. **Digitalisasi bisnis Anda dengan solusi custom end-to-end.**\n\nGw rekomendasiin nomor **4** — singkat, jelas, langsung nyambung ke isi paketnya.\n\nMau pake yang mana atau mau gw bikin versi lain?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":226,"cacheRead":36359,"cacheWrite":342,"totalTokens":36930,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0056500000000000005,"cacheRead":0.018179499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.0021375,"total":0.025981999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775022137944}}
