{"type":"message","id":"ba256b49","parentId":"972b108e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:44:42.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, dari gambarnya gw liat ada beberapa clue — ada attendance (clock-in/out), face recognition, dan dashboard web. Gw buatin fitur HRIS yang standar + sesuai visual brosurnya:\n\n---\n\n**Tagline:**\n*Kelola SDM perusahaan dari mana saja, kapan saja.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Absensi mobile dengan GPS & face recognition\n• Clock-in / clock-out real-time\n• Dashboard admin & laporan kehadiran\n• Manajemen data karyawan lengkap\n• Pengajuan cuti & izin online\n• Slip gaji digital & perhitungan payroll\n• Jadwal shift & rotasi otomatis\n• Rekap lembur & keterlambatan\n• Notifikasi & pengumuman karyawan\n• Akses web & mobile app (Android/iOS)\n• Garansi sistem 2 tahun\n• Technical support 2 tahun\n\n---\n\nAtau kalau space-nya terbatas kayak yang FMS tadi, versi compact:\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Absensi GPS & face recognition\n• Clock-in/out real-time via mobile\n• Dashboard admin & laporan kehadiran\n• Manajemen data karyawan & payroll\n• Pengajuan cuti, izin & lembur online\n• Jadwal shift & rotasi otomatis\n• Slip gaji digital & rekap bulanan\n• Notifikasi & pengumuman internal\n• Akses web & mobile (Android/iOS)\n• Garansi & support 2 tahun\n\n---\n\nPilih yang panjang atau compact? Atau mau adjust?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":421,"cacheRead":36701,"cacheWrite":1121,"totalTokens":38246,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.010525000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0183505,"cacheWrite":0.00700625,"total":0.03589675}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775022272816}}
