{"type":"message","id":"383d728d","parentId":"3ef9f2f8","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:46:07.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, Safety Attribute Detection System — AI CCTV buat deteksi APD (Alat Pelindung Diri) di area kerja.\n\n---\n\n**Tagline:**\n*Pastikan keselamatan kerja dengan deteksi APD otomatis berbasis AI.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• 1x Kamera AI deteksi atribut keselamatan\n• Deteksi otomatis: helm, safety belt, sepatu safety & rompi\n• Alert real-time saat pekerja tanpa APD lengkap\n• 1x Starlink Gen 3 untuk konektivitas remote site\n• 1x Solar Panel (operasi mandiri tanpa listrik PLN)\n• 2x Repeater untuk jangkauan sinyal optimal\n• Adapter + mounting & kabel extender\n• Instalasi lengkap di lokasi\n• Dashboard monitoring & rekap pelanggaran\n• Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n---\n\nVersi compact kalau space kecil:\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Kamera AI deteksi helm, safety belt, sepatu & rompi\n• Alert real-time pelanggaran APD\n• 1x Starlink Gen 3 + 1x Solar Panel\n• 2x Repeater + adapter & mounting\n• Instalasi lengkap & kabel extender\n• Dashboard monitoring & rekap\n• Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n---\n\nMau pake yang mana?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":367,"cacheRead":36701,"cacheWrite":1963,"totalTokens":39034,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.009175,"cacheRead":0.0183505,"cacheWrite":0.01226875,"total":0.03980925}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775022358752}}
