{"type":"message","id":"fbc71776","parentId":"c2f78ad1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:51:17.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nWah ini produk AI server on-premise ya — Sistem SentrAI. Yang sekarang cuma 5 bullet, terlalu generic. Gw bikin lebih spesifik dan menjual:\n\n---\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Server high-end (lokal/cloud) siap pakai\n• Sistem AI on-premise — data tetap di server Anda\n• Enkripsi & keamanan data enterprise-grade\n• Instalasi server, jaringan & konfigurasi\n• Instalasi software AI & integrasi sistem\n• Custom AI model sesuai kebutuhan bisnis\n• Dashboard monitoring & manajemen\n• Backup otomatis & disaster recovery\n• Pelatihan tim operasional & admin\n• Technical support & maintenance 1 tahun\n\n---\n\nVersi compact:\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Server high-end (lokal/cloud) siap pakai\n• AI on-premise — data 100% di server Anda\n• Enkripsi & keamanan enterprise-grade\n• Instalasi server, software & integrasi\n• Custom AI model sesuai kebutuhan\n• Dashboard monitoring & backup otomatis\n• Pelatihan & support 1 tahun\n\n---\n\nBtw harga 50 juta buat on-premise AI server itu *very competitive*. Itu termasuk hardware-nya atau software doang?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":343,"cacheRead":36701,"cacheWrite":3114,"totalTokens":40161,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.008575000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0183505,"cacheWrite":0.0194625,"total":0.046403}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775022668150}}
