{"type":"message","id":"02f531a9","parentId":"4a763dfd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:53:45.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, dua paket Starlink. Tagline-nya juga perlu dibenerin — yang sekarang nggak nyambung. Nih:\n\n---\n\n**STARLINK HOME ULTRA PACKAGE**\n\n*Koneksi internet cepat & stabil untuk kantor dan rumah.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• 1x Starlink Gen 3\n• 2x Repeater TP-Link (jangkauan Wi-Fi maksimal)\n• Kecepatan download hingga 200 Mbps\n• Jangkauan sinyal seluruh area kantor/rumah\n• Adapter + mounting + kabel\n• Instalasi & konfigurasi jaringan\n• Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp. 7.950.000,00 / Set**\n\n---\n\n**STARLINK ENTERPRISE PACKAGE**\n\n*Internet mandiri untuk remote site — tanpa listrik PLN, tanpa kabel.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• 1x Starlink Gen 3\n• 1x Solar Panel VIGI (operasi off-grid)\n• Konektivitas di lokasi terpencil (tambang, perkebunan, proyek)\n• Operasi 24/7 tanpa ketergantungan PLN\n• Adapter + mounting + kabel\n• Instalasi & konfigurasi lengkap\n• Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp. 17.750.000,00 / Set**\n\n---\n\nYang gw benerin:\n- **Home Ultra** — tagline lama \"kantor yang memiliki\" nggak lengkap, gw ganti\n- **Enterprise** — tagline lama \"penggunaan ringan & mobile\" nggak cocok buat paket 17.7 juta dengan solar panel, harusnya nge-highlight remote/off-grid\n\nMau adjust?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":467,"cacheRead":36701,"cacheWrite":4456,"totalTokens":41627,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.011675000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0183505,"cacheWrite":0.02785,"total":0.0578905}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775022813765}}
