{"type":"message","id":"1a200edf","parentId":"1ace0dcb","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:18:36.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n**TELEMATICS**\n\nTeltonika Heavy-Duty Gateway — otak utama FMS di dalam kendaraan. Mengirim data mesin, konsumsi BBM, dan lokasi secara real-time ke Dashboard FMS Sentra.\n\n**Spesifikasi :**\n• CAN-Bus Ready — tarik data RPM & Hour Meter langsung dari mesin\n• Multi-Sensor Port — mendukung sensor BBM akurasi tinggi & sensor hidrolik\n• Dual-SIM LTE — koneksi tetap stabil di area blank spot\n• Industrial Grade — casing metal tahan getaran alat berat & debu pekat\n• GPS Tracking — posisi & riwayat perjalanan real-time\n• Monitoring BBM — pantau konsumsi & deteksi kebocoran/pengurasan\n• ADAS (Advanced Driver Assistance) — peringatan tabrakan, lane departure & jarak aman\n• Plug & Play — instalasi cepat tanpa modifikasi kendaraan\n\n---\n\nMau gw tambahin lagi atau udah pas?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":268,"cacheRead":26276,"cacheWrite":16883,"totalTokens":43430,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0067,"cacheRead":0.013137999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.10551875000000001,"total":0.12537175}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775024311214}}
