{"type":"message","id":"e69c8e46","parentId":"82797d36","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:21:15.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nWah iya sorry bro, gw liat sekarang — teksnya nabrak ke bawah, overlapping sama elemen lain. Gw bikin ulang yang lebih pendek:\n\n---\n\n**Spesifikasi :**\n• CAN-Bus Ready (RPM & Hour Meter)\n• Multi-Sensor (BBM & hidrolik)\n• Dual-SIM LTE (anti blank spot)\n• Industrial Grade (tahan getar & debu)\n• GPS Tracking real-time\n• Monitoring BBM & deteksi kebocoran\n• ADAS (peringatan tabrakan & lane)\n• Plug & Play\n\n---\n\nTiap bullet 1 baris pendek, nggak bakal overflow. Coba masukin ini?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":191,"cacheRead":43159,"cacheWrite":860,"totalTokens":44213,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004775000000000001,"cacheRead":0.021579499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.0053750000000000004,"total":0.031744499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775024469356}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ff8a000","parentId":"e69c8e46","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:55:18.106Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-01 06:51:37 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:51:42 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:52:42 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:52:45 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:53:45 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:53:48 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:54:48 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 06:54:51 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB031738060FD575A83D9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nhmm apa kamu bisa bantu aku untuk edit canva, maksudku kamu yang edit, dan menggunakan pc ku"}],"timestamp":1775026518099}}
{"type":"message","id":"be66e92d","parentId":"3ff8a000","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:55:30.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHmm, technically gw bisa remote ke PC lo kalau lo punya OpenClaw node app yang paired — tapi itu ribet setupnya dan Canva itu UI-heavy banget (drag & drop, resize, layer management). Bakal lambat dan error-prone.\n\nYang lebih realistis:\n\n**Opsi 1 — Lo paste, gw kasih teks yang udah fix**\nKayak yang kita lakuin sekarang. Lo copy-paste ke Canva, kirim screenshot, gw feedback. Ini paling cepat.\n\n**Opsi 2 — Gw bikin versi brosurnya dari nol**\nGw bikin HTML/PDF yang designnya mirip brosur Sentra lo, teks udah bener semua, lo tinggal export atau kasih ke desainer.\n\n**Opsi 3 — Remote PC lo**\nBisa, tapi perlu install OpenClaw companion app di Mac lo, pair ke server, terus gw control browser-nya. Setup ~15-20 menit dan hasilnya nggak bakal se-smooth lo edit sendiri.\n\nGw rekomendasiin tetep **Opsi 1** — kita udah flow bagus, tinggal lanjut aja. Atau kalau lo mau yang lebih polished, gw bisa bikin full brosur layout baru (**Opsi 2**).\n\nMau yang mana?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":354,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":44638,"totalTokens":44995,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00885,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.2789875,"total":0.2878525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775026518103}}
