{"type":"message","id":"add02124","parentId":"3a5fd0d2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:59:57.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNah ini udah bagus! 1 halaman, 1 produk, clean. Tapi ada beberapa yang perlu diperbaiki:\n\n**Yang perlu dibenerin:**\n\n1. **Tagline** — \"Solusi Pemantauan Armada Alat Berat & Data Mesin Real-Time.\" ✅ udah oke\n\n2. **Bullet ke-3 overflow** — \"Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi otomatis\" kepotong jadi 2 baris. Pendekin jadi: \"Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi\"\n\n3. **Space bawah kosong banget** — antara bullet terakhir dan harga ada gap gede. Bisa tambahin 1-2 bullet lagi atau geser harga naik\n\n**Saran tambahan bullet (opsional, isi space kosong):**\n• Laporan maintenance & jadwal servis\n• Analitik kesehatan mesin via CAN-Bus\n\n**Soal harga — 518 juta itu buat berapa unit?** Kalau itu paket 50 unit (sesuai demo tadi), mungkin bagus ditambahin keterangan: \"*untuk 50 unit kendaraan*\" atau \"*harga disesuaikan jumlah armada*\" biar klien nggak kaget liat angka.\n\nJadi versi final:\n\n---\n\n*Solusi Pemantauan Armada Alat Berat & Data Mesin Real-Time.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Dashboard real-time & live GPS tracking\n• Laporan ritase, BBM & performa armada\n• Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi\n• Live streaming CCTV & face recognition\n• Geofence, panic alert & heatmap\n• Analitik kesehatan mesin via CAN-Bus\n• Laporan maintenance & jadwal servis\n• Akses multi-device (desktop, tablet, HP)\n\n---\n\nMau pake 8 bullet atau tetep 6?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":513,"cacheRead":45166,"cacheWrite":1786,"totalTokens":47468,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.012825000000000001,"cacheRead":0.022583,"cacheWrite":0.0111625,"total":0.046585499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775026778687}}
