{"type":"message","id":"c22fe5c1","parentId":"cd8b4727","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:06:06.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSpace kosong gede di antara bullet terakhir dan harga. Ada beberapa opsi:\n\n**Opsi A — Tambahin bullet (paling gampang)**\n\nTambahin 3-4 bullet lagi biar ngisi:\n\n• Analitik kesehatan mesin via CAN-Bus\n• Laporan maintenance & jadwal servis\n• Notifikasi otomatis & alert system\n• Garansi & technical support 1 tahun\n\nJadi total 10 bullet, space keisi rata.\n\n**Opsi B — Tambahin paragraf singkat**\n\nDi bawah bullet, tambahin 1-2 kalimat deskripsi:\n\n*\"Satu platform terintegrasi untuk seluruh kebutuhan monitoring armada. Dari lokasi, performa mesin, hingga keselamatan pengemudi — semua terpantau real-time dari satu dashboard.\"*\n\n**Opsi C — Geser elemen**\n\nGeser screenshot-nya naik (lebih besar), atau geser harga naik. Biar space merata, nggak numpuk di satu area.\n\n**Rekomendasi gw: Opsi A + C**\n\nTambahin 3-4 bullet DAN geser harga naik sedikit. Hasilnya:\n\n---\n\n**Termasuk :**\n• Dashboard real-time & live GPS tracking\n• Laporan ritase, BBM & performa armada\n• Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi\n• Live streaming CCTV & face recognition\n• Geofence, panic alert & heatmap\n• Analitik kesehatan mesin via CAN-Bus\n• Laporan maintenance & jadwal servis\n• Notifikasi otomatis & alert system\n• Akses multi-device (desktop, tablet, HP)\n• Garansi & technical support 1 tahun\n\n---\n\n10 bullet, space keisi, nggak ada gap kosong. Coba?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":491,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":47771,"totalTokens":48265,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.012275000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.29856875,"total":0.31085875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775027141095}}
