{"type":"message","id":"ffb9cc6f","parentId":"6d15222b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:18:14.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke gw dapet transcript-nya. Ini video dari **Liam Ottley** (YouTuber AI/agency) bareng co-host Mark, ngebahas **OpenClaw (ClawdBot)** dan 3 cara bikin duit dari situ.\n\n**Ringkasan:**\n\nVideo ini ngebahas OpenClaw — tool open-source yang bikin Claude Code bisa diakses dari mana aja (WhatsApp, Telegram, Slack, Discord), bukan cuma terminal. Intinya kayak *air traffic control* buat AI.\n\n**3 cara bikin duit yang disebut:**\n1. **Jasa setup OpenClaw buat orang/bisnis** — banyak orang mau pake tapi nggak bisa setup sendiri. Lo charge buat instalasi + konfigurasi.\n2. **Bikin & jual custom skills** — OpenClaw modular, lo bisa bikin skill khusus dan jual/lisensi ke user lain.\n3. **Build AI agency pakai OpenClaw** — pake sebagai backbone buat service bisnis lo (automasi, personal assistant, dll).\n\n**Key points:**\n- Bisa jalan di cloud (AWS free tier), Mac Mini, atau Docker — nggak harus mahal\n- Bisa pake model apa aja (Gemini lebih murah dari Anthropic)\n- Open source = fully customizable\n- Mereka bilang ada \"arbitrage window\" 6-12 bulan sebelum mainstream catch up\n\nIni relevan sama setup lo sekarang — lo literally udah running OpenClaw. Mau gw breakdown lebih detail atau ada pertanyaan spesifik?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":412,"cacheRead":60397,"cacheWrite":3122,"totalTokens":63932,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0103,"cacheRead":0.0301985,"cacheWrite":0.019512500000000002,"total":0.060016}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775031479686}}
