aya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi Display Cloud\n• Hosting konten & scheduling\n• Update software\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\n**INTERACTIVE DISPLAY — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi software\n• Update & maintenance\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\n**TELEMATICS — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 500.000/bulan** per unit\n• SIM card data\n• Akses dashboard & tracking\n• Update firmware\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\n**STARLINK — semua paket**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per set\n• Langganan internet Starlink\n• Monitoring koneksi\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\n**SURVEILLANCE — Start From Rp 850.000/titik**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 500.000/bulan** per titik\n• Cloud storage rekaman\n• AI detection processing\n• Monitoring & alert\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\nAngka-angka ini lo bisa adjust ke atas/bawah sesuai margin yang Nabil mau. Mau gw naikin lagi atau ada produk tertentu yang perlu diubah?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":993,"cacheRead":68095,"cacheWrite":1190,"totalTokens":70281,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.024825,"cacheRead":0.0340475,"cacheWrite":0.0074375000000000005,"total":0.06632500000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775033898134}}
