{"type":"message","id":"b7e532d4","parentId":"e17a057f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:58:57.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNoted. Tambang batubara Kaltim — revenue miliaran per bulan. Harga yang gw kasih tadi *kemurahan* buat market ini. Mereka nggak mikirin jutaan, mereka mikir efisiensi dan compliance.\n\nGw revisi — pricing premium buat mining sector:\n\n---\n\n**EKOSISTEM FMS — Start From Rp 518.350.000**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 35.000.000/bulan**\n• Lisensi platform FMS enterprise\n• Dedicated server & cloud infrastructure\n• SIM card data seluruh unit armada\n• NOC monitoring 24/7 (Network Operations Center)\n• SLA response time < 4 jam\n• Update software, security patch & compliance report\n• Backup & disaster recovery\n• Account manager dedicated\n\n*Opsi bulanan: Rp 85.000.000/bulan (12 bulan, all-inclusive)*\n\n---\n\n**HRIS — Start From Rp 418.350.000**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 25.000.000/bulan**\n• Lisensi platform & mobile app unlimited user\n• Dedicated server & infrastructure\n• Compliance reporting (Disnaker, BPJS, PPh 21)\n• SLA response time < 4 jam\n• Update fitur & security patch\n• Backup harian & disaster recovery\n• Account manager dedicated\n\n*Opsi bulanan: Rp 65.000.000/bulan (12 bulan, all-inclusive)*\n\n---\n\n**SAFETY ATTRIBUTE DETECTION — Start From Rp 1.250.000/titik**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 7.500.000/bulan** per titik\n• Langganan konektivitas Starlink\n• AI processing & real-time analytics\n• Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n• Dashboard HSE reporting (K3)\n• Maintenance kamera, solar panel & repeater\n• Monitoring & alert 24/7\n• SLA response time < 4 jam\n\n---\n\n**SISTEM SentrAI — Start From Rp 50.350.000**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 15.000.000/bulan**\n• Maintenance server & jaringan on-site\n• AI model retraining & optimization berkala\n• Backup & disaster recovery\n• Monitoring performa 24/7\n• Dedicated compute resources\n• Security audit bulanan\n• Account manager dedicated\n\n*Opsi bulanan: Rp 20.000.000/bulan (12 bulan, all-inclusive)*\n\n---\n\n**SMART LOCK — Start From Rp 750.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi app & cloud monitoring\n• Log akses & audit trail (compliance)\n• Update firmware & security patch\n• Replacement key card\n• Technical support priority\n\n---\n\n**TELEMATICS — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.250.000/bulan** per unit\n• SIM card data dedicated\n• Dashboard tracking & analytics\n• Update firmware & ADAS calibration\n• Technical support priority\n\n---\n\n**SURVEILLANCE — Start From Rp 850.000/titik**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per titik\n• Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n• AI detection & analytics\n• Monitoring & alert 24/7\n• Maintenance & cleaning berkala\n\n---\n\n**DIGITAL SIGNBOARD — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 3.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi Display Cloud\n• Content management & scheduling\n• Maintenance & cleaning\n• Technical support\n\n---\n\n**INTERACTIVE DISPLAY — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 3.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi software enterprise\n• Update & maintenance\n• Technical support priority\n\n---\n\n**STARLINK — semua paket**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 2.500.000/bulan** per set\n• Langganan internet Starlink\n• Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n• Troubleshooting & maintenance\n• SLA uptime 95%+\n\n---\n\nBuat konteks: tambang dengan 50 unit hauler yang ambil full FMS package, total bulanannya sekitar **Rp 85-100 juta/bulan**. Buat perusahaan tambang yang revenue-nya miliaran, itu *nothing* — kurang dari 1% revenue. Dan itu yang bikin pricing ini justified.\n\nMau gw adjust lagi atau ini udah bisa di-forward ke Nabil?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":1196,"cacheRead":69285,"cacheWrite":1163,"totalTokens":71647,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.029900000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0346425,"