{"type":"message","id":"f1b8e298","parentId":"2038e20b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:59:47.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nIya lo bener — Rp 7.5 juta/bulan per titik itu kegedean kalau klien pasang banyak titik. 20 titik aja udah 150 juta/bulan cuma buat kamera APD.\n\nYang bikin mahal itu sebenernya *Starlink-nya*, bukan kamera AI-nya. Jadi harusnya dipisah:\n\n---\n\n**SAFETY ATTRIBUTE DETECTION — Start From Rp 1.250.000/titik**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 2.000.000/bulan** per titik\n• AI processing & analytics\n• Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n• Dashboard HSE / K3 reporting\n• Maintenance kamera\n• Monitoring & alert 24/7\n• Technical support\n\n*Catatan: Biaya konektivitas Starlink terpisah (lihat paket Starlink)*\n\n---\n\nJadi kamera AI-nya Rp 2 juta/bulan per titik — itu lebih masuk akal. Kalau titik-nya pake Starlink, klien bayar Starlink-nya terpisah Rp 2.5 juta/bulan. Kalau titik-nya udah ada internet (WiFi/LAN), ya cuma Rp 2 juta aja.\n\nLebih make sense?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":344,"cacheRead":70448,"cacheWrite":1402,"totalTokens":72197,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0086,"cacheRead":0.035224,"cacheWrite":0.008762500000000001,"total":0.052601499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775033978824}}
