nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.250.000/bulan** per unit\n• SIM card data dedicated\n• Dashboard tracking & analytics\n• Update firmware & ADAS calibration\n• *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n**SURVEILLANCE — Start From Rp 850.000/titik**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 1.500.000/bulan** per titik\n• Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n• AI detection & analytics\n• Monitoring & alert 24/7\n• Maintenance & cleaning berkala\n• *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n**DIGITAL SIGNBOARD — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 3.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi Display Cloud\n• Content management & scheduling\n• Maintenance & cleaning\n• *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n**INTERACTIVE DISPLAY — Start From Rp 6.850.000/unit**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 3.500.000/bulan** per unit\n• Lisensi software enterprise\n• Update & maintenance\n• *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n**STARLINK — semua paket**\nBiaya bulanan: **Rp 2.500.000/bulan** per set\n• Langganan internet Starlink\n• Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n• Troubleshooting & maintenance\n• *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\nSemua seragam: bayar bulanan = dapat support selamanya. Stop bayar = stop support. Simple, clean, gampang dijual.\n\nOke gini atau mau adjust?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":1053,"cacheRead":71850,"cacheWrite":509,"totalTokens":73415,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.026325,"cacheRead":0.035925,"cacheWrite":0.00318125,"total":0.06544625}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034008955}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2617f3d","parentId":"25a1ab67","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:01:28.109Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0864BCB427F2D8E7A57\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nbuatkan aku dokumentasinya, kalau bisa brosur tdi kamu adjust semua pointnya, kamu edit saja, kalo tidak bisa docs aja gamasalah"}],"timestamp":1775034088098}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf0caedd","parentId":"d2617f3d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:02:28.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGw nggak bisa edit file Canva lo langsung, tapi gw bikin dokumen lengkap yang tinggal lo copy ke Canva atau forward ke Nabil."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_UoJxhU5bnVE2QIyMMfdzDo","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/sentra-brosur-update.md","content":"# SENTRA TECHNOLOGY — Katalog Produk & Pricing (Updated)\n\n---\n\n## 1. EKOSISTEM FMS\n**Solusi Pemantauan Armada Alat Berat & Data Mesin Real-Time.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- Dashboard real-time & live GPS tracking\n- Laporan ritase, BBM & performa armada\n- Monitoring perilaku supir & intervensi\n- Live streaming CCTV & face recognition\n- Geofence, panic alert & heatmap\n- Analitik kesehatan mesin via CAN-Bus\n- Laporan maintenance & jadwal servis\n- Notifikasi otomatis & alert system\n- Akses multi-device (Desktop, Tablet, HP)\n\n**Start From: Rp 518.350.000**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 35.000.000/bulan**\n- Lisensi platform FMS enterprise\n- Dedicated server & cloud infrastructure\n- SIM card data seluruh unit armada\n- NOC monitoring 24/7\n- SLA response time < 4 jam\n- Update software & security patch\n- Backup & disaster recovery\n- Account manager dedicated\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 2. HUMAN RESOURCE INFORMATION SYSTEM (HRIS)\n**Kelola SDM perusahaan dari mana saja, kapan saja.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- Absensi mobile dengan GPS & face recognition\n- Clock-in / clock-out real-time\n- Dashboard admin & laporan kehadiran\n- Manajemen data karyawan lengkap\n- Pengajuan cuti & izin online\n- Slip gaji digital & perhitungan payroll\n- Jadwal shift & rotasi otomatis\n- Rekap lembur & keterlambatan\n- Notifikasi & pengumuman karyawan\n- Akses web & mobile app (Android/iOS)\n\n**Start From: Rp 418.350.000**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 25.000.000/bulan**\n- Lisensi platform & mobile app unlimited user\n- Dedicated server & infrastructure\n- Compliance reporting (Disnaker, BPJS, PPh 21)\n- Update fitur & security patch\n- Backup harian & disaster recovery\n- Account manager dedicated\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 3. SAFETY ATTRIBUTE DETECTION SYSTEM\n**Pastikan keselamatan kerja dengan deteksi APD otomatis berbasis AI.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Kamera AI deteksi atribut keselamatan\n- Deteksi otomatis: helm, safety belt, sepatu safety & rompi\n- Alert real-time saat pekerja tanpa APD lengkap\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3 untuk konektivitas remote site\n- 1x Solar Panel (operasi mandiri tanpa listrik PLN)\n- 2x Repeater untuk jangkauan sinyal optimal\n- Adapter + mounting & kabel extender\n- Instalasi lengkap di lokasi\n- Dashboard monitoring & rekap pelanggaran\n\n**Start From: Rp 1.250.000/titik**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.000.000/bulan per titik**\n- AI processing & analytics\n- Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n- Dashboard HSE / K3 reporting\n- Maintenance kamera\n- Monitoring & alert 24/7\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n- *Catatan: Biaya konektivitas Starlink terpisah (lihat paket Starlink)*\n\n---\n\n## 4. SISTEM SentrAI\n**AI Cerdas. Data Aman. Semua di Server Anda.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- Server high-end (lokal/cloud) siap pakai\n- Sistem AI on-premise — data tetap di server Anda\n- Enkripsi & keamanan data enterprise-grade\n- Instalasi server, jaringan & konfigurasi\n- Development dan instalasi software AI & integrasi sistem\n- Custom AI model sesuai kebutuhan bisnis\n- Dashboard monitoring & manajemen\n- Backup otomatis & disaster recovery\n- Pelatihan tim operasional & admin\n\n**Start From: Rp 50.350.000**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 15.000.000/bulan**\n- Maintenance server & jaringan on-site\n- AI model retraining & optimization berkala\n- Backup & disaster recovery\n- Monitoring performa 24/7\n- Security audit bulanan\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 5. SMART LOCK SYSTEM\n**Keamanan kantor terpindai dan terawasi.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- Aplikasi monitoring akses real-time\n- Integrasi ke aplikasi keamanan yang ada\n- Security lock untuk gerbang, pintu & gate\n- +10 Key Card per unit\n- Akses via PIN, kartu, fingerprint & app\n- Log riwayat akses masuk/keluar\n- Notifikasi otomatis akses tidak sah\n- Request akses digital (approval via app)\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n\n**Start From: Rp 750.000/unit**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 1.500.000/bulan per unit**\n- Lisensi app & cloud monitoring\n- Log akses & audit trail\n- Update firmware & security patch\n- Replacement key card\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 6. TELEMATICS\n**Teltonika Heavy-Duty Gateway — otak utama FMS di dalam kendaraan.**\n\n**Spesifikasi :**\n- CAN-Bus Ready (RPM & Hour Meter)\n- Multi-Sensor (BBM & hidrolik)\n- Dual-SIM LTE (anti blank spot)\n- Industrial Grade (tahan getar & debu)\n- GPS Tracking real-time\n- Monitoring BBM & deteksi kebocoran\n- ADAS (peringatan tabrakan & lane)\n- DVR (Kamera Driver)\n- Plug & Play\n\n**Start From: Rp 6.850.000/unit**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 1.250.000/bulan per unit**\n- SIM card data dedicated\n- Dashboard tracking & analytics\n- Update firmware & ADAS calibration\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 7. SURVEILLANCE COVERAGE\n**TP-Link VIGI AI Surveillance Series — ekosistem kamera AI terintegrasi.**\n\n**Spesifikasi :**\n- Varian Komprehensif: Dome, Bullet, PTZ, Solar Panel Mandiri\n- Smart AI Detection: Otomatis mengenali manusia, kendaraan & anomali\n- Full-Color Night Vision: Resolusi tinggi, tetap berwarna meski gelap\n- Industrial Weatherproof: Standar IP67, tahan debu & cuaca ekstrem\n\n**Start From: Rp 850.000/titik**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 1.500.000/bulan per titik**\n- Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n- AI detection & analytics\n- Monitoring & alert 24/7\n- Maintenance & cleaning berkala\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 8. DIGITAL SIGNBOARD\n**Signboard digital menampilkan video dinamis dengan teks, gambar, dan video real-time.**\n\n**Fitur utama :**\n- Layar Full HD / 4K\n- Dukungan untuk gambar, video, HTML5, dan live stream\n- Manajemen konten jarak jauh melalui Display Cloud\n- Timer otomatis dan penjadwalan harian\n- Opsi tampilan vertikal atau horizontal\n\n**Start From: Rp 6.850.000/unit**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 3.500.000/bulan per unit**\n- Lisensi Display Cloud\n- Content management & scheduling\n- Maintenance & cleaning\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 9. INTERACTIVE DISPLAY\n**Perangkat layar interaktif besar untuk meeting, pembelajaran, dan presentasi digital.**\n\n**Fitur utama :**\n- Resolusi Full HD hingga 4K\n- Ukuran 86–100 inci, cocok untuk ruang besar\n- Touch Screen multi-sentuh responsif\n- Sistem operasi berbasis Android TV atau Windows\n- Konektivitas universal dengan berbagai perangkat\n\n**Start From: Rp 6.850.000/unit**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 3.500.000/bulan per unit**\n- Lisensi software enterprise\n- Update & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 10. STARLINK HOME STARTER PACKAGE\n**Internet satelit siap pakai — simple & praktis.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 6.850.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 11. STARLINK HOME BASIC PACKAGE\n**Cocok untuk kantor kecil & rumah dengan jangkauan lebih luas.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 1x Wi-Fi Repeater\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 7.450.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 12. STARLINK HOME ULTRA PACKAGE\n**Koneksi internet cepat & stabil untuk kantor dan rumah.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 2x Repeater TP-Link\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi jaringan\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 7.950.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 13. STARLINK ENTERPRISE PACKAGE\n**Internet mandiri untuk remote site — tanpa listrik PLN, tanpa kabel.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 1x Solar Panel VIGI\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi lengkap\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 17.750.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 14. STARLINK SOLAR COVERAGE PACKAGE\n**Internet mandiri tanpa PLN — ideal untuk remote site.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 1x Solar Panel (operasi off-grid)\n- 1x Repeater (perluasan sinyal)\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 18.350.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## 15. STARLINK SOLAR COVERAGE MAX PACKAGE\n**Coverage maksimal di lokasi terpencil — tambang, perkebunan, proyek.**\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 1x Solar Panel (operasi off-grid 24/7)\n- 2x Repeater (jangkauan area luas)\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n- Gratis layanan 1 bulan\n\n**Rp 19.250.000/set**\n\n**Biaya Bulanan: Rp 2.500.000/bulan**\n- Langganan internet Starlink\n- Monitoring koneksi & uptime report\n- Troubleshooting & maintenance\n- *Lifetime support selama berlangganan*\n\n---\n\n## RINGKASAN PRICING\n\n| Produk | Harga Unit/Paket | Bulanan |\n|--------|-----------------|---------|\n| Ekosistem FMS | Rp 518.350.000 | Rp 35.000.000/bln |\n| HRIS | Rp 418.350.000 | Rp 25.000.000/bln |\n| Safety Attribute Detection | Rp 1.250.000/titik | Rp 2.000.000/bln/titik |\n| Sistem SentrAI | Rp 50.350.000 | Rp 15.000.000/bln |\n| Smart Lock | Rp 750.000/unit | Rp 1.500.000/bln/unit |\n| Telematics | Rp 6.850.000/unit | Rp 1.250.000/bln/unit |\n| Surveillance | Rp 850.000/titik | Rp 1.500.000/bln/titik |\n| Digital Signboard | Rp 6.850.000/unit | Rp 3.500.000/bln/unit |\n| Interactive Display | Rp 6.850.000/unit | Rp 3.500.000/bln/unit |\n| Starlink (semua paket) | Rp 6.850.000 - 19.250.000/set | Rp 2.500.000/bln/set |\n\n**Semua biaya bulanan termasuk lifetime support selama berlangganan.**\n\n---\n\n*PT. Sentra Visi Teknologi*\n*+62 822 5544 3380 | info@sentratechnology.com*\n*www.sentratechnology.com*\n*Kompleks Graha Indah Blok A 13, Samarinda, Kalimantan Timur*\n"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":3932,"cacheRead":72359,"cacheWrite":1250,"totalTokens":77544,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0983,"cacheRead":0.036179499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0078125,"total":0.142307}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775034088105}}
