{"type":"message","id":"96eacaf2","parentId":"f288b90d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:03:12.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Udah gw kirim file-nya. Isinya:\n\n- **15 produk** lengkap — semua tagline, fitur, dan harga udah di-update\n- **Harga bulanan baru** yang realistis buat market tambang\n- **Lifetime support** di setiap produk\n- **Tabel ringkasan pricing** di bagian akhir\n\nTinggal copy-paste ke Canva per section, atau forward langsung ke Nabil buat review. Mau gw adjust sesuatu lagi?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":136,"cacheRead":79080,"cacheWrite":411,"totalTokens":79628,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0034000000000000002,"cacheRead":0.03954,"cacheWrite":0.0025687500000000003,"total":0.04551375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034186694}}
