{"type":"message","id":"45b86cd4","parentId":"18c69392","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:11:18.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBingung di bagian mana spesifik? Gw tebak beberapa kemungkinan:\n\n**1. Harga Rp 1.250.000/titik itu buat apa aja?**\nSatu \"titik\" itu = 1 kamera AI di 1 lokasi. Tapi di brosur lo juga include Starlink + Solar Panel + 2 Repeater — itu harusnya bukan per titik, itu *paket infrastruktur*. Jadi sekarang kacau — harga per titik tapi isinya paket besar.\n\n**2. Masalah utamanya:**\nBrosur lo nyampur 2 hal:\n- **Kamera AI** (per titik) = murah, bisa banyak\n- **Infra konektivitas** (Starlink + Solar + Repeater) = mahal, biasanya 1 set per area\n\n**Saran gw — pisah jadi 2 tier:**\n\n---\n\n**SAFETY DETECTION — KAMERA AI**\n*Per titik kamera, butuh koneksi internet existing.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Kamera AI deteksi APD\n- Deteksi helm, safety belt, sepatu & rompi\n- Alert real-time pelanggaran APD\n- Instalasi & konfigurasi\n\n**Start From: Rp 1.250.000/titik**\n**Bulanan: Rp 2.000.000/bulan per titik**\n\n---\n\n**SAFETY DETECTION — PAKET REMOTE SITE**\n*Untuk lokasi tanpa internet & listrik PLN.*\n\n**Termasuk :**\n- 1x Kamera AI deteksi APD\n- 1x Starlink Gen 3\n- 1x Solar Panel\n- 2x Repeater\n- Adapter + mounting + kabel\n- Instalasi lengkap\n\n**Start From: Rp 22.500.000/set**\n**Bulanan: Rp 4.500.000/bulan per set**\n\n---\n\nJadi klien yang udah ada internet cuma bayar kamera aja (murah). Klien di remote site yang butuh Starlink + solar bayar paket lengkap.\n\nLebih masuk akal nggak gitu?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":583,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":79790,"totalTokens":80376,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.014575000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.4986875,"total":0.5132775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034664185}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f8d9c71","parentId":"45b86cd4","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:11:56.561Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0966D8FD9F684F95F2A\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nDiminta detailkan sama sistem sistem nya, dari hardware dan juga sistem"}],"timestamp":1775034716552}}
{"type":"message","id":"4e4c8870","parentId":"1f8d9c71","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:12:24.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke, full breakdown hardware + software:\n\n---\n\n## SAFETY ATTRIBUTE DETECTION SYSTEM — Detail Teknis\n\n### HARDWARE\n\n**Kamera AI**\n- Kamera IP dengan built-in AI processor (edge computing)\n- Resolusi minimum 2MP (1080p), rekomendasi 4MP\n- Lensa wide-angle (120°+) untuk coverage area luas\n- Night vision / IR untuk operasi 24 jam\n- Rating IP67 (tahan debu & air)\n- Mounting bracket + tiang (outdoor/indoor)\n\n**Starlink Gen 3**\n- Antena flat phased-array\n- Download hingga 200 Mbps\n- Latency 20-40ms\n- Power consumption ~75W\n- Mounting kit + kabel 15m\n\n**Solar Panel**\n- Kapasitas minimum 200W\n- Controller MPPT\n- Baterai LiFePO4 (backup 8-12 jam)\n- Tiang mounting + bracket\n- Kabel & konektor weatherproof\n\n**Repeater (2x)**\n- TP-Link outdoor access point\n- Range hingga 500m per unit\n- PoE powered\n- IP65 weatherproof\n- Mounting bracket + kabel\n\n**Tambahan**\n- Adapter PoE\n- Kabel extender (CAT6 outdoor, 50-100m)\n- Junction box & connector\n- Grounding kit (petir)\n\n---\n\n### SISTEM / SOFTWARE\n\n**AI Detection Engine**\n- Model computer vision terlatih khusus APD Indonesia\n- Deteksi objek: helm, rompi safety, safety belt, sepatu safety, kacamata\n- Akurasi deteksi: 90%+ dalam kondisi normal\n- Processing di edge (kamera) — tidak tergantung cloud\n- Waktu respon deteksi: < 2 detik\n\n**Alert System**\n- Notifikasi real-time via dashboard, email & WhatsApp/Telegram\n- Alarm audio/visual di lokasi (opsional, buzzer + lampu)\n- Eskalasi otomatis: pekerja → supervisor → HSE manager\n- Log foto pelanggaran + timestamp + lokasi\n\n**Dashboard Monitoring**\n- Web-based, akses dari browser manapun\n- Live feed kamera\n- Rekap pelanggaran harian/mingguan/bulanan\n- Statistik per area, per shift, per pekerja\n- Export laporan PDF/Excel\n- Grafik tren kepatuhan APD\n\n**Penyimpanan & Data**\n- Cloud storage rekaman 90 hari\n- Backup otomatis harian\n- Data terenkripsi (AES-256)\n- Akses role-based (admin, supervisor, viewer)\n\n**Integrasi**\n- API untuk integrasi ke sistem HSE existing\n- Compatible dengan CCTV/NVR existing\n- Export data ke format standar K3\n\n---\n\n### FLOW KERJA SISTEM\n\n```\nPekerja masuk area → Kamera AI scan → APD lengkap? \n  ├─ YA → Log OK, lanjut\n  └─ TIDAK → Alert real-time → Supervisor notified \n             → Foto + detail masuk dashboard\n             → Rekap masuk laporan HSE\n```\n\n---\n\n### SPESIFIKASI MINIMUM PER TITIK\n\n| Komponen | Qty | Keterangan |\n|----------|-----|------------|\n| Kamera AI | 1 | Edge processing, IP67 |\n| PoE Adapter | 1 | Power over Ethernet |\n| Mounting + bracket | 1 set | Outdoor rated |\n| Kabel CAT6 outdoor | 50m | Weatherproof |\n| Junction box | 1 | IP65 |\n\n**Tambahan untuk remote site (tanpa internet & PLN):**\n\n| Komponen | Qty | Keterangan |\n|----------|-----|------------|\n| Starlink Gen 3 | 1 | Konektivitas internet |\n| Solar Panel + baterai | 1 set | 200W + LiFePO4 |\n| Repeater outdoor | 2 | Coverage area luas |\n| Grounding kit | 1 | Proteksi petir |\n\n---\n\nMau gw kirim sebagai file juga, atau ini udah cukup buat lo copy ke Nabil?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":1082,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":80543,"totalTokens":81628,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.02705,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.50339375,"total":0.53045875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034716558}}
