{"type":"message","id":"bc40fca7","parentId":"9117b63f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:14:11.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBener juga — ini terlalu detail buat brosur. Gw ringkasin biar muat di 1 halaman brosur:\n\n---\n\n**SAFETY ATTRIBUTE DETECTION SYSTEM**\n*Deteksi APD otomatis berbasis AI — langsung di lokasi kerja.*\n\n**Hardware :**\n• Kamera AI IP67 (edge processing, 1080p+)\n• Night vision 24 jam\n• Starlink Gen 3 (remote site)\n• Solar Panel 200W + baterai backup\n• 2x Repeater outdoor (jangkauan 500m)\n• PoE adapter, mounting & kabel\n\n**Sistem :**\n• Deteksi helm, rompi, safety belt, sepatu & kacamata\n• Alert real-time (dashboard, WhatsApp & email)\n• Dashboard HSE: rekap pelanggaran & statistik\n• Cloud storage 90 hari\n• Export laporan K3 (PDF/Excel)\n• Integrasi ke sistem HSE existing\n\n**Harga :**\n\n| Paket | Harga | Bulanan |\n|-------|-------|---------|\n| Kamera AI (per titik) | Rp 1.250.000 | Rp 2.000.000/bln |\n| Paket Remote Site (1 kamera + Starlink + Solar + 2 Repeater) | Rp 22.500.000 | Rp 4.500.000/bln |\n\n*Lifetime support selama berlangganan.*\n\n---\n\nIni muat di 1 halaman brosur, ada hardware, sistem, DAN harga 2 tier. Klien langsung ngerti bedanya — punya internet tinggal pasang kamera, remote site ambil paket lengkap.\n\nMau pake ini?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":453,"cacheRead":79790,"cacheWrite":2007,"totalTokens":82253,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.011325,"cacheRead":0.039895,"cacheWrite":0.012543750000000001,"total":0.06377875000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775034839955}}
