er untuk jangkauan sinyal optimal\nAdapter + mounting & kabel extender\nInstalasi lengkap di lokasi\nDashboard monitoring & rekap pelanggaran\nGratis layanan 1 bulan\n\nOne Time Buy\n\nRP. 1.250.000,00\n\n/ Titik\n\n*Exclude Server\n\nBulanan\n\nRP. 2.000.000,OO\n\n/Titik\n\n*Include Server\n\nSISTEM SentrAI\nAI Cerdas. Data Aman. Semua di Server Anda.\nTermasuk :\nServer high-end (lokal/cloud) siap pakai\nSistem AI on-premise — data tetap di server Anda\nEnkripsi & keamanan data enterprise-grade\nInstalasi server, jaringan & konfigurasi\nDevelopment dan Installasi software AI &\nintegrasi sistem\nCustom AI model sesuai kebutuhan bisnis\nDashboard monitoring & manajemen\nBackup otomatis & disaster recovery\nPelatihan tim operasional & admin\nTechnical support & maintenance 1 tahun\nStart From\n\nRP. 50.350.000,00\nRP. 15.000.000,OO /Month\n\nSMART LOCK SYSTEM\nKemanana Kantor terpindai dan terawasi\nTermasuk :\nAplikasi monitoring akses real-time\nIntegrasi ke aplikasi keamanan yang ada\nSecurity lock untuk gerbang, pintu & gate\n+10 Key Card per unit\nAkses via PIN, kartu, fingerprint & app\nLog riwayat akses masuk/keluar\nNotifikasi otomatis akses tidak sah\nRequest akses digital (approval via app)\nInstalasi & konfigurasi\nGaransi 1 Tahun\nTechnical Support 1 Tahun\n\nStart From\n\nRP. 750.OOO,00\n\n/ Unit\n\nRP. 1.000.000,OO /Month\n\nThank You!\n\nOur Contact:\n+62 822-5544-3380\n\nwww.sentratechnology.com\n\nsentratechnologyid@gmail.com\n\nPerum Graha Indah Blok A,\nSamarinda, Kalimantan Timur","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775038086443}}
{"type":"message","id":"f93616ee","parentId":"31a9ca92","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:08:23.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke gw udah baca versi terbaru. Bagus, udah banyak yang ke-update! Gw kasih feedback:\n\n**Yang udah bagus ✅**\n- FMS: Rp 35 juta/bln ✅\n- HRIS: Rp 25 juta/bln ✅\n- SentrAI: Rp 15 juta/bln ✅\n- Safety Detection: split exclude/include server ✅ smart move\n- Telematics: dipecah 5 hardware (CAN reader, TPMS, Telematics, Fuel Sensor, ADAS) ✅\n- Harga Digital Signboard & Interactive Display udah naik ✅\n- \"Lifetime Support untuk Berlangganan bulanan\" ✅\n\n**Yang masih perlu dibenerin ⚠️**\n\n1. **Smart Lock — masih Rp 1.000.000/bln** ← ini kan placeholder yang mau dihapus? Ganti **Rp 1.500.000/bln per unit**\n\n2. **Surveillance — nggak ada harga bulanan** sama sekali. Tambahin **Rp 1.500.000/bln per titik**\n\n3. **Starlink — masih Rp 1.000.000/bln** ← ini bisa dipertahanin kalau emang cuma pass-through Starlink subscription, atau naikin ke **Rp 2.500.000/bln** kalau include monitoring & support\n\n4. **Digital Signboard & Interactive Display — nggak ada harga bulanan.** Tambahin **Rp 3.500.000/bln per unit**\n\n5. **Telematics — nggak ada harga bulanan.** Tambahin di bawah semua hardware: **Rp 1.250.000/bln per unit** (SIM card, dashboard, firmware update, lifetime support)\n\n6. **Typo: \"Kemanana\"** → harusnya **\"Keamanan\"** (Smart Lock tagline)\n\n7. **Safety Detection** — masih include Starlink + Solar + Repeater di bullet points, tapi tadi kita sepakat exclude jaringan? Atau ini sengaja tetep di situ?\n\nMau gw update dokumen-nya lagi dengan semua fix ini?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":591,"cacheRead":84121,"cacheWrite":2780,"totalTokens":87493,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.014775,"cacheRead":0.0420605,"cacheWrite":0.017375,"total":0.0742155}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775038086451}}
