{"type":"message","id":"23f83f70","parentId":"43a0e53e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:18:37.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_G96uH4WkkKNMEzWQ1uYh5B","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  function resetView() { mapState.zoom = 1; mapState.panX = 0; mapState.panY = 0; }\n\n  function toggleGrid() {\n    mapState.showGrid = !mapState.showGrid;\n    $('#map-grid-toggle')?.classList.toggle('active', mapState.showGrid);\n    debounceSaveMap();\n  }\n\n  function toggleSnap() {\n    mapState.snapToGrid = !mapState.snapToGrid;\n    $('#map-snap-toggle')?.classList.toggle('active', mapState.snapToGrid);\n  }\n\n  function toggleMeasure() {\n    mapState.measuring = !mapState.measuring;\n    $('#map-measure-btn')?.classList.toggle('active', mapState.measuring);\n    mapState.measureStart = null;\n    mapState.measureEnd = null;\n    $('#map-measure-label')?.classList.add('hidden');\n    $('#map-canvas-wrap')?.classList.toggle('measuring', mapState.measuring);\n\n[6432 more lines in file. Use offset=2450 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775056717467}}
{"type":"message","id":"0273bfb2","parentId":"23f83f70","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:18:42.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ha — `toggleSnap` nggak panggil `debounceSaveMap()`! Dan `snapToGrid` nggak ada di `getSerializableState()`. Tapi ini bukan masalah utama.\n\nGw cek token move — apakah setelah drag, save dipanggil:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_D73u0f2P7YdtOskzTcilWC","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":2340,"path":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":179,"cacheRead":107350,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":107942,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004475,"cacheRead":0.053675,"cacheWrite":0.002575,"total":0.06073}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775056717478}}
{"type":"message","id":"190a9d0a","parentId":"0273bfb2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:18:42.880Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_D73u0f2P7YdtOskzTcilWC","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    }\n  }\n\n  function onMouseUp() {\n    const wrap = $('#map-canvas-wrap');\n\n    if (mapState.fogDrawing && mapState.fogDrawStart && mapState.fogDrawCurrent) {\n      const s = mapState.fogDrawStart, c = mapState.fogDrawCurrent;\n      const x = Math.min(s.x, c.x), y = Math.min(s.y, c.y);\n      const w = Math.abs(c.x - s.x), h = Math.abs(c.y - s.y);\n      if (w > 5 && h > 5) {\n        const rect = { x, y, w, h };\n        mapState.fogReveals.push(rect);\n        broadcastFogReveal(rect);\n        debounceSaveMap();\n      }\n      mapState.fogDrawing = false;\n      mapState.fogDrawStart = null;\n      mapState.fogDrawCurrent = null;\n      wrap?.classList.remove('fog-drawing');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (mapState.draggingToken) {\n      broadcastTokenMove(mapState.draggingToken);\n      debounceSaveMap();\n      mapState.draggingToken = null;\n      wrap?.classList.remove('dragging-token');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    mapState.panning = false;\n  }\n\n  function onWheel(e) {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    const delta = e.deltaY > 0 ? -0.1 : 0.1;\n    const pos = getCanvasPos(e);\n    zoomAt(pos.x, pos.y, delta);\n  }\n\n[6502 more lines in file. Use offset=2380 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775056722874}}
{"type":"message","id":"97d0aae4","parentId":"190a9d0a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:18:50.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke — token drag → `broadcastTokenMove` + `debounceSaveMap`. Tapi `broadcastTokenMove` hanya sends `{ id, x, y }` via websocket, sedangkan `debounceSaveMap` saves ENTIRE map state (termasuk tokens) via HTTP POST.\n\nFlow ini seharusnya works. Tapi masalahnya mungkin `loadMapState` yang nggak bener restore token positions saat page load. Gw cek lagi `handleWSMapUpdate`:\n\nData yang di-save: `{ tokens: [...], gridSize, showGrid, fogEnabled, fogReveals, bgImageUrl }`\nData yang di-load: same object → `handleWSMapUpdate` → tokens + grid restored.\n\nHmm, ini harusnya kerja. Kecuali — gw cek apakah ada race condition atau bug lain:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_HMLXHlIkoM2iSuwhwNrRaG","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"snapToGrid\\|gridSize\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js | head -20","timeout":5}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":311,"cacheRead":107762,"cacheWrite":620,"totalTokens":108694,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.007775000000000001,"cacheRead":0.053881,"cacheWrite":0.003875,"total":0.065536}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775056722882}}
