{"type":"message","id":"c6cf9266","parentId":"b7ddb6d8","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:19:45.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! Gw udah fix bug-nya. Ini yang gw ubah:\n\n**Backend (server.js):**\n- `token_move` sekarang **persist ke rooms.json** (sebelumnya cuma broadcast, nggak save)\n- `map_update` sekarang **persist** juga\n- Tambahin handler baru: `grid_update`, `token_add`, `token_remove` — semua persist\n- `fog_reveal` sekarang **persist**\n- Tambahin REST API: `/api/rooms/:pin/grid`, `/api/rooms/:pin/tokens`, `/api/rooms/:pin/battlemap`\n\n**Frontend (app.js):**\n- `snapToGrid` sekarang di-save dan di-load (sebelumnya hilang saat refresh)\n- Debounce save dipercepat: 3 detik → 1 detik\n- Tambahin `beforeunload` handler — auto-save saat tutup/refresh page (pakai `sendBeacon`)\n\nCoba refresh page-nya, geser token, ubah grid, terus refresh lagi — harusnya sekarang persistent. 🎲"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":283,"cacheRead":111363,"cacheWrite":295,"totalTokens":111942,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0070750000000000006,"cacheRead":0.055681499999999995,"cacheWrite":0.0018437500000000001,"total":0.06460525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056776392}}
