{"type":"message","id":"ac01b9ed","parentId":"c78b754d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:20:11.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ada free API dan database buat D&D 5e SRD. Gw punya 2 pendekatan:\n\n**Approach 1 — Integrate 5e SRD API (recommended)**\nPake `https://www.dnd5eapi.co` — free REST API, no auth needed. Udah punya:\n- Semua spells, monsters, classes, races, equipment, feats\n- Searchable, filterable\n- JSON format — gampang integrate ke web kita\n\n**Approach 2 — Mirror 5e.tools**\nDownload source data-nya (mereka open source di GitHub), host di server kita. Lebih lengkap tapi *jauh* lebih berat.\n\nGw rekomendasiin **Approach 1** — tambahin tab \"Compendium\" di DnD app kita yang connect ke 5e SRD API. Include:\n- **Spells browser** — search, filter by class/level/school\n- **Monsters/Bestiary** — search, filter by CR/type\n- **Items & Equipment** — weapons, armor, magic items\n- **Classes & Races** — full descriptions & features\n- **AI Character Generator** — pake data dari API buat auto-generate characters\n\nIni lumayan besar — mau gw mulai sekarang atau lo mau gw prioritasin yang mana dulu (compendium browser atau AI character generator)?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056811326}}
