{"type":"message","id":"1c58ee44","parentId":"462cb0cd","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:21:03.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mantap — **nggak perlu scrape**. Data-nya udah ada dalam JSON format, siap pakai. 4.5MB total:\n\n- **Spells** (320+ spells)\n- **Monsters** (300+ monsters)\n- **Classes & Subclasses**\n- **Races/Species**\n- **Equipment & Magic Items**\n- **Feats, Skills, Conditions**\n- **2014 (5e classic) + 2024 (5e revised)**\n\nJadi plannya:\n\n1. Copy JSON data ke `/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/srd/`\n2. Tambahin API endpoints di backend buat serve data\n3. Bikin \"Compendium\" tab di frontend — search & browse semua data\n4. Hook ke AI character generator — pull real spells, equipment, dll\n\nGw mulai sekarang?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":217,"cacheRead":115072,"cacheWrite":409,"totalTokens":115699,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005425,"cacheRead":0.057536,"cacheWrite":0.00255625,"total":0.06552224999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056855132}}
