{"type":"message","id":"534ad0e7","parentId":"c772c144","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:22:17.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Subagent udah jalan. Dia lagi:\n1. Copy SRD data ke server\n2. Bikin API endpoints buat serve spells, monsters, classes, dll\n3. Bikin Compendium tab di frontend\n4. Hook ke AI character generator\n\nIni bakal butuh beberapa menit. Gw kabarin begitu selesai. Sambil nunggu, ada yang lain mau dikerjain?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":108,"cacheRead":115852,"cacheWrite":1130,"totalTokens":117091,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0027,"cacheRead":0.057926,"cacheWrite":0.0070625,"total":0.0676935}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056930139}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e784c9d","parentId":"534ad0e7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:28:17.618Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0262178C033123CA8D9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nalso, buatkan versi terjemahan bahasa indonesianya"}],"timestamp":1775057297599}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a3050d7","parentId":"5e784c9d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:28:31.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNoted — tambahin terjemahan Bahasa Indonesia buat semua data Compendium. Gw spawn satu lagi subagent buat handle translation setelah compendium-nya selesai, atau mau gw masukin ke task yang sama?\n\nSebenernya, biar lebih efisien gw tambahin aja ke subagent yang lagi jalan — toggle bahasa (EN/ID) di UI."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_3GstAyWEqzhzkznRwe268c","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"label":"dnd-compendium","message":"ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENT: Add Indonesian (Bahasa Indonesia) translation support.\n\n1. Add a language toggle button (EN/ID) in the Compendium tab header\n2. Translate all UI labels, section headers, filter names to Indonesian\n3. For the SRD data content: add translated descriptions where feasible. At minimum:\n   - Spell names: keep English name + add Indonesian description/summary\n   - Monster names: keep English + add type in Indonesian (e.g., \"Dragon\" → \"Naga\")\n   - Class descriptions: translate to Indonesian\n   - Equipment: translate descriptions, keep English name\n   - Conditions: translate name + description fully to Indonesian\n   - Skills: translate descriptions to Indonesian\n4. Store translations in a separate JSON file (e.g., /data/srd/translations-id.json) so it's easy to maintain\n5. Default language: Indonesian (ID), with toggle to switch to English\n6. The toggle should persist in localStorage\n\nKeep it simple — don't over-translate game mechanics terms that players usually keep in English (like \"hit points\", \"armor class\", ability score names). Focus on descriptions and flavor text."}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":438,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":117253,"totalTokens":117694,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.01095,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWri