{"type":"message","id":"fa754fbc","parentId":"c7e27b76","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:18:05.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ini **D&D 5e Player's Handbook 2024** — full book dalam format flipbook.\n\nLo mau ini juga di-embed atau di-reference di web DnD kita? Ada beberapa opsi:\n\n**Opsi 1 — Embed flipbook langsung**\nTambahin tab \"Rulebook\" di web kita, embed anyflip viewer via iframe. Paling gampang, tapi tergantung anyflip tetep online.\n\n**Opsi 2 — Download & host sendiri**\nAmbil PDF-nya, host di server kita, bikin reader sendiri. Nggak tergantung pihak ketiga.\n\n**Opsi 3 — Reference link aja**\nTambahin button \"📖 Player's Handbook\" di compendium yang buka link anyflip di tab baru.\n\nGw rekomendasiin **Opsi 1** — embed iframe di tab baru \"Rulebook\". Cepet, works, dan player bisa flip-flip langsung dari app kita.\n\nMau gw tambahin sekarang?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":272,"cacheRead":119033,"cacheWrite":624,"totalTokens":119930,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0068000000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0595165,"cacheWrite":0.0039000000000000003,"total":0.0702215}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775063875424}}
