{"type":"message","id":"826f7cc1","parentId":"2d1cb67a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:20:14.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semua jalan. SRD data loaded (319 spells, 334 monsters, 12 classes, dll) + translations ID.\n\nDone! Tab **📖 Rulebook** udah live di web DnD lo. Player's Handbook 2024 full book embedded langsung di app.\n\nPlus, **📚 Compendium** juga udah selesai dibangun sama subagent — complete dengan:\n- 319 spells, 334 monsters, 12 classes, 9 races, dll\n- Terjemahan Bahasa Indonesia\n- Toggle EN/ID\n- Search & filter\n\nCoba buka web-nya dan cek tab Rulebook + Compendium 🎲"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":175,"cacheRead":125817,"cacheWrite":982,"totalTokens":126975,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004375,"cacheRead":0.06290849999999999,"cacheWrite":0.006137500000000001,"total":0.07342599999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775064007065}}
{"type":"message","id":"6288a621","parentId":"826f7cc1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:00:58.058Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/f7ffa99e-e790-4fb3-9784-63933d9a9518.jpg (image/jpeg)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:56:23 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:56:27 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:57:27 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:57:30 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:58:30 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:58:33 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:59:33 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 17:59:36 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\nSystem: [2026-04-01 18:00:36 UTC] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-01 18:00:40 UTC] WhatsApp gateway connected as +6281938953639.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0203EC62D20F5F06BEC\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\naku mau kayak gini, di web kita gada spell dkk"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1775066458027}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f5b413f","parentId":"6288a621","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:01:14.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGw liat — lo mau tampilan kayak 5e.tools yang detail banget: class features per level, subclass breakdown, spell details, semua dalam 1 page scrollable dengan sidebar navigation.\n\nCompendium kita sekarang masih basic — cuma cards dengan summary. Yang lo mau itu *full reference page* kayak 5e.tools.\n\nMasalahnya, data SRD yang kita punya (dari 5e-database) itu **SRD only** — cuma subset kecil. 5e.tools punya data dari *semua* sourcebook (PHB, DMG, Xanathar's, Tasha's, dll) — itu jauh lebih lengkap.\n\nAda 2 opsi:\n\n**Opsi 1 — Clone 5e.tools langsung**\nDownload source code mereka dari GitHub, host di server kita sebagai halaman terpisah. Lo dapet *exact* same experience kayak screenshot itu. Paling cepat dan paling lengkap.\n\n**Opsi 2 — Rebuild dari nol di app kita**\nBikin UI mirip 5e.tools tapi di dalam tab DnD app kita. Butuh waktu lebih lama dan data tetep terbatas ke SRD.\n\nGw rekomendasiin **Opsi 1** — clone & host 5e.tools di server kita, terus embed atau link dari app. Lo dapet semua data lengkap tanpa gw harus rebuild semuanya.\n\nMau gw lakukan?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":384,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":128752,"totalTokens":129139,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.009600000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.8047000000000001,"total":0.8143150000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775066458047}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbf00316","parentId":"6f5b413f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:03:22.797Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB061F770F8851D65A7DF\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nui nya dibuat bagus, newbie friendly, ui mu bagus so far, kurang konten aja"}],"timestamp":1775066602772}}
{"type":"message","id":"68130866","parentId":"bbf00316","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:03:32.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke paham — UI kita udah bagus, yang kurang itu **konten yang lengkap dan detail**. Jadi plannya:\n\n1. **Clone data 5e.tools** (semua spells, classes, monsters, items dari semua sourcebook)\n2. **Tambahin ke compendium kita** dengan UI yang udah ada (yang emang bagus)\n3. **Detail page per item** yang lengkap — bukan cuma summary card, tapi full breakdown kayak 5e.tools\n\nGw kerjain sekarang."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_8EW2ixjhx9CoO2O9MV2ChU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/5etools-mirror-3/5etools-src.git 2>&1 | tail -5","timeout":120,"yieldMs":90000}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":267,"cacheRead":126799,"cacheWrite":1358,"totalTokens":128427,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.006675,"cacheRead":0.0633995,"cacheWrite":0.0084875,"total":0.078577}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775066602789}}
