{"type":"message","id":"915ececd","parentId":"8e5f98c7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:04:58.921Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Subagent lagi kerjain upgrade besar-besaran. Yang bakal berubah:\n\n**Konten:**\n- 319 spells → **900+ spells** (semua sourcebook)\n- 334 monsters → **4,454 monsters**\n- 12 classes → **15 classes** (termasuk Artificer, Mystic)\n- Items, feats, races — semua jauh lebih lengkap\n\n**Detail view yang baru:**\n- **Spells** — casting time, range, components, duration, full description, \"At Higher Levels\"\n- **Monsters** — full stat block classic D&D style (tan box, red dividers, abilities, actions, legendary)\n- **Classes** — features per level, subclasses, spell lists\n- **Items** — rarity, attunement, properties\n\n**Performance:**\n- Pagination (50 per halaman)\n- Server-side filtering\n- Debounced search\n\nIni bakal butuh beberapa menit karena data-nya gede. Gw kabarin begitu live 👍"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":260,"cacheRead":129983,"cacheWrite":1544,"totalTokens":131788,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.006500000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0649915,"cacheWrite":0.00965,"total":0.0811465}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775066689619}}
