{"type":"message","id":"c2f8adf4","parentId":"05ac0a40","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:07:58.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nIya, deskripsi kontennya masih English — yang ke-translate cuma label UI (header, kategori, filter). Deskripsi spells, items, monsters itu dari data SRD asli yang emang English.\n\nMasalahnya: ada **900+ spells, 4400+ monsters, ratusan items** — translate semua secara manual nggak realistis.\n\nTapi gw bisa bikin **auto-translate on-the-fly** pake AI. Jadi waktu user klik item, deskripsi-nya di-translate ke Indo otomatis dan di-cache biar nggak translate ulang.\n\nMau gw tambahin fitur itu? Atau lo prefer gw translate batch yang paling penting dulu (misal top 100 spells, common items, semua conditions)?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":207,"cacheRead":131527,"cacheWrite":818,"totalTokens":132555,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.005175,"cacheRead":0.0657635,"cacheWrite":0.0051125,"total":0.07606600000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775066869678}}
