{"type":"message","id":"ac74cd64","parentId":"ef68dc1c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:10:31.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! Sekarang kalau bahasa di-set ke ID (🇮🇩) dan lo klik spell/monster/item:\n\n1. Detail muncul dalam English dulu\n2. Otomatis **\"🔄 Menerjemahkan...\"** muncul di tiap deskripsi\n3. Setelah selesai, teks berubah ke **Bahasa Indonesia**\n4. Ada toggle **\"🇬🇧 Original\"** kalau mau liat versi English\n5. Hasil translate di-**cache** — klik item yang sama nggak perlu translate ulang\n\nCoba klik salah satu spell di Compendium dengan bahasa ID aktif!\n\nNote: subagent yang lagi upgrade ke 4400+ monsters masih jalan. Begitu selesai, semua konten baru juga bakal auto-translate."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":217,"cacheRead":139706,"cacheWrite":982,"totalTokens":140906,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005425,"cacheRead":0.069853,"cacheWrite":0.006137500000000001,"total":0.0814205}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775067022264}}
