{"type":"message","id":"c78406ad","parentId":"dc7a66fa","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:10:45.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNoted — fokus data dari **Player's Handbook 2024 (XPHB)** aja, bukan semua sourcebook. Gw steer subagent yang lagi jalan:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_n5ohUOTbVWv1QLsmxLUuDv","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"steer","target":"dnd-content-upgrade","message":"IMPORTANT UPDATE: Focus ONLY on Player's Handbook 2024 (XPHB) data. Do NOT include all sourcebooks.\n\nSpecifically:\n- Spells: ONLY from spells-xphb.json (391 spells)\n- Classes: All 12 PHB 2024 classes with full features + subclasses\n- Races/Species: PHB 2024 species only\n- Equipment: PHB 2024 equipment\n- Feats: PHB 2024 feats\n- Backgrounds: PHB 2024 backgrounds\n- Conditions: PHB 2024 conditions\n\nFilter source field = \"XPHB\" where applicable. If the 5etools data has a \"source\" field, only include entries where source === \"XPHB\" or \"PHB\" (for 2024 edition).\n\nDo NOT load 4400 monsters from all books — only include monsters/creatures referenced in PHB 2024 if any. The focus is on player-facing content, not DM bestiary.\n\nThis keeps the data focused, relevant, and manageable."}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":395,"cacheRead":140688,"cacheWrite":396,"totalTokens":141482,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.009875,"cacheRead":0.070344,"cacheWrite":0.002475,"total":0.082709}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775067032673}}
