{"type":"message","id":"feccb89e","parentId":"9da2bd0d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:24:18.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Compendium upgrade udah selesai dan translation masih jalan (lagi di feats sekarang). Update:\n\n**Compendium udah live dengan data PHB 2024 lengkap:**\n\n| Kategori | Jumlah |\n|----------|--------|\n| Spells | 391 |\n| Classes | 12 (283 features, 48 subclasses) |\n| Equipment | 221 items |\n| Feats | 81 |\n| Conditions | 24 |\n| Species | 12 |\n| Backgrounds | 27 |\n\n**Detail view yang baru:**\n- **Spells** — casting time, range, components + material detail, duration, concentration/ritual badges, \"At Higher Levels\", class tags\n- **Classes** — proficiencies, features per level (bisa expand/collapse), subclasses dengan nested features\n- **Items** — type, cost, weight, damage, AC, property badges\n- **Feats** — category badge (General/Origin/Fighting Style/Epic Boon), prerequisites\n- **Species** — speed, size, darkvision, traits, subraces\n- **Backgrounds** — skill/tool proficiencies\n\n**Performance:**\n- Load More pagination (50 per batch)\n- Server-side filtering\n- Debounced search\n\nTranslation progress: ✅ Conditions done, ✅ Backgrounds done, 🔄 Feats lagi jalan, ⏳ Spells (391) next. Gw kabarin lagi kalau semua translate selesai.\n\nCoba refresh web-nya sekarang!"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":387,"cacheRead":144572,"cacheWrite":304,"totalTokens":145264,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.009675000000000001,"cacheRead":0.072286,"cacheWrite":0.0019,"total":0.08386600000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775067849592}}
